◆ decrReaction()

void decrReaction ( const double *const  p_s,
double *const  p_r 
) const
inlineinherited

Performs the following operation on this reaction:

\[ r_j = r_j - \sum_{i=1}^{n_s} \nu_{ij} s_i \]

where \(r_j\) is a reaction dependent quantity, \(s_i\) are species dependent quantities, and \(\nu_{ij}\) is the stoichiometric coefficient for species i in reaction j.

Performs the following operation on the species in this reaction:

\[ s_i = s_i - \nu_{ij} r_j, \quad \forall \; i = 1,\dots,n_s \]

where \(r_j\) is a reaction dependent quantity, \(s_i\) are species dependent quantities, and \(\nu_{ij}\) is the stoichiometric coefficient for species i in reaction j.

◆ multReaction()

void multReaction ( const double *const  p_s,
double *const  p_r 
) const
inlineinherited

Performs the following operation on this reaction:

\[ r_j = r_j \prod_{i=1}^{n_s} s_i^{\nu_{ij}} \]

where \(r_j\) is a reaction dependent quantity, \(s_i\) are species dependent quantities, and \(\nu_{ij}\) is the stoichiometric coefficient for species i in reaction j.
